## Common Issues

### "Failed to fetch pool data"
- Check backend is running on port 5000
- Verify CORS is enabled
- Check Llama API availability

### Empty tables
- Verify filters aren't too strict
- Check if API returned data
- Log pool count to debug

### Stale cache
- Cache is SQLite on disk тАФ it persists across restarts
- Delete `packages/server/src/data/cache.db` to force a full re-fetch on next startup

